  <brief_title>A Study to Evaluate the Analgesic Efficacy and Safety of VM902A in Subjects With Osteoarthritis (OA) of the Knee</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled and Active-controlled, Parallel-group Study Evaluating the Analgesic Efficacy and Safety of VM902A in Subjects With Moderate to Severe Chronic Pain Due to Osteoarthritis of the Knee</official_title>
