  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the analgesic efficacy, safety, and tolerability of
      VM902A twice daily compared to placebo in subjects with moderate to severe chronic pain due
      to OA of the knee.
    </textblock>
